CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774828709
OL,3,CSwinney to push for powers over energy
OL,4,Cif SNP wins election
OL,6,FFirst Minister John Swinney will push
OL,7,Fthe UK Government for Holyrood control
OL,8,Fover energy policy if his party wins
OL,9,FMay's election, he has said.
OL,11,FSpeaking ahead of a visit to the north-
OL,12,Feast of Scotland, Mr Swinney said an
OL,13,FSNP-run government ` which would be
OL,14,Freturned to power after a fifth
OL,15,Fstraight election victory ` would
OL,16,Fdraft a Section 30 order that would
OL,17,Fgive the Scottish Parliament powers
OL,18,Fover energy on the first day after his
OL,19,Fre-election as First Minister.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774828709
OL,3,CSwinney to push for powers over energy
OL,4,Cif SNP wins election
OL,6,FSection 30 of the Scotland Act allows
OL,7,Fthe UK Government to devolve powers to
OL,8,FHolyrood and was used to allow the
OL,9,FScottish Parliament to legislate for
OL,10,Fthe independence referendum in 2014.
OL,12,FGiven the value of Scotland's energy `
OL,13,Fparticularly the oil and gas in the
OL,14,FNorth Sea ` the UK Government is
OL,15,Fextremely unlikely to grant such a
OL,16,Fmove, which the First Minister said
OL,17,Fwould confirm that Scottish
OL,18,Findependence is the only way to bring
OL,19,Fdown household bills.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774828709
OL,3,CSwinney to push for powers over energy
OL,4,Cif SNP wins election
OL,6,FIf the SNP was to make the request on
OL,7,Fthe first day of the new parliamentary
OL,8,Fterm, it would do so without a
OL,9,Ffinalised energy strategy being
OL,10,Fproduced by the Government.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
