CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774828709
OL,3,CSwinney to push for powers over energy
OL,4,Cif SNP wins election
OL,6,FThe document was published in draft
OL,7,Fform under Nicola Sturgeon ` including
OL,8,Fa presumption against new oil and gas
OL,9,F` but never finalised, with a
OL,10,Fspokesman for the First Minister last
OL,11,Fweek blaming the volatility in the
OL,12,Fglobal sector and the party's
OL,13,FWestminster leader Stephen Flynn
OL,14,Fsaying confusion caused by the UK
OL,15,FGovernment made it difficult to
OL,16,Fproduce a plan.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
