OL,3,CSwinney to push for powers over energy
OL,4,Cif SNP wins election
OL,6,FSpeaking ahead of the visit, the First
OL,7,FMinister said: "Scotland is one of the
OL,8,Fmost energy rich countries in the
OL,9,Fworld ` but we pay some of the highest
OL,10,Fbills in Europe.
OL,12,F"That is because for decades,
OL,13,FScotland's energy wealth has flowed
OL,14,Fsouth to the Treasury rather than
OL,15,Fworking for the people of Scotland.
OL,17,F"UK Government control over our energy
OL,18,Fresources is seeing bills soar, jobs
OL,19,Fdestroyed and key energy investment
OL,20,Fprojects denied.
OL,26,@oD@POUtD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774828709
OL,3,CSwinney to push for powers over energy
OL,4,Cif SNP wins election
OL,6,F"Westminster control is not working
OL,7,Ffor energy security, it is not working
OL,8,Ffor jobs and it is not working for
OL,9,Fpeople's bills. By every measure
OL,10,FWestminster has failed."
OL,12,FThe First Minister has said a majority
OL,13,Ffor his party in May would secure a
OL,14,Fmandate for a second referendum on
OL,15,Findependence, but added: "The process
OL,16,Fof a referendum will take time, so I
OL,17,Fwant to begin the journey to
OL,18,Findependence on day one of the new
OL,19,Fterm with the immediate transfer of
OL,20,Fpowers over our energy.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@XO]wD@ZOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774828709
OL,3,CSwinney to push for powers over energy
OL,4,Cif SNP wins election
OL,6,F"Because Westminster's abject failures
OL,7,Fare really hurting people now `
OL,8,Fcosting jobs and seeing bills soar. So
OL,9,FI want to be able to take action now.
OL,11,F"If Westminster will not act to bring
OL,12,Fdown bills, they should get out of the
OL,13,Fway for a government that will. It's
OL,14,FScotland's energy ` and it should be
OL,15,Fin Scotland's hands.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774828709
OL,3,CSwinney to push for powers over energy
OL,4,Cif SNP wins election
OL,6,F"And if the UK Government refuse, it
OL,7,Fwill only confirm that if we want to
OL,8,Fmake Scotland's energy wealth work for
OL,9,FScotland and bring down bills, that is
OL,10,Fonly available through the fresh start
OL,11,Fof independence that I am offering at
OL,12,Fthis election."
OL,14,FScottish Tory energy spokesman Douglas
OL,15,FLumsden said the First Minister's
OL,16,Fpledge was "designed to mask two
OL,17,Fdecades of failure".
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@OO]xD@LOUyD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774828709
OL,3,CSwinney to push for powers over energy
OL,4,Cif SNP wins election
OL,6,F"He's part of the reason why Scots'
OL,7,Fenergy bills are rising right now. He
OL,8,Fshamefully turned his back on our oil
OL,9,Fand gas industry by blocking new
OL,10,Fprojects such as Rosebank and Jackdaw
OL,11,Fin the North Sea," he said.
OL,13,F"And he continues to have a reckless
OL,14,Fand ideological ban on new nuclear
OL,15,Fpower too.
OL,17,F"His rush for mega-pylons threatens to
OL,18,Fdecimate the landscape of rural
OL,19,FScotland and the nationalists continue
OL,20,Fto ride roughshod over local
OL,21,Fopposition.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@RO]uD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774828709
OL,3,CSwinney to push for powers over energy
OL,4,Cif SNP wins election
OL,6,F"Instead of whipping up more
OL,7,Fnationalist grievance, John Swinney
OL,8,Fshould ditch his failing energy policy
OL,9,Fand support plans that protect jobs
OL,10,Fand grow Scotland's economy."
OL,12,FWhile Scottish Labour finance
OL,13,Fspokesman Michael Marra said the First
OL,14,FMinister "has no energy ` let alone a
OL,15,Fserious plan for Scotland's".
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@]O]vD@JOUwD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774828709
OL,3,CSwinney to push for powers over energy
OL,4,Cif SNP wins election
OL,6,F"The SNP has squandered Scotland's
OL,7,Fclean energy potential for years `
OL,8,Fditching its plans for a publicly-
OL,9,Fowned energy company, selling off
OL,10,FScotland's seabeds on the cheap and
OL,11,Fbreaking its green jobs pledge," he
OL,12,Fadded.
OL,14,F"They can't build a ferry, they can't
OL,15,Frun our NHS and they can't be trusted
OL,16,Fto keep their promises.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@`O]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774828709
OL,3,CSwinney to push for powers over energy
OL,4,Cif SNP wins election
OL,6,F"John Swinney is not remotely serious
OL,7,Fabout this half-baked plan ` he just
OL,8,Fwants to avoid talking about this own
OL,9,Frecord which has left Scots paying
OL,10,Fmore and getting less."
OL,12,FUK Tory leader Kemi Badenoch will also
OL,13,Fcampaign in the north-east on Monday,
OL,14,Falongside her party's leader in
OL,15,FScotland Russell Findlay, following
OL,16,Fthe launch of the party's "get Britain
OL,17,Fdrilling" campaign, which calls for
OL,18,Fthe end to the UK Government's ban on
OL,19,Fnew oil and gas licences and an end to
OL,20,Fthe windfall tax.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@WO]xD@[OUyD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
