CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774828709
OL,3,CSwinney to push for powers over energy
OL,4,Cif SNP wins election
OL,6,FThe party is also calling for VAT on
OL,7,Fenergy bills to be scrapped, along
OL,8,Fwith the levies imposed on electricity
OL,9,Fgeneration and subsidies for wind
OL,10,Fdevelopments, with the aim of cutting
OL,11,Fbills by #200.
OL,13,F"I know families and business owners
OL,14,Facross Britain will be very worried
OL,15,Fabout how the global energy crisis
OL,16,Fwill impact them," she said.
OL,18,F"That's why I find it appalling that
OL,19,FLabour's solution is to tax working
OL,20,Fpeople to fund a bailout for those on
OL,21,Fbenefits.
OL,26,@uD@AOUxD@RO]zD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30514
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774828709
OL,3,CSwinney to push for powers over energy
OL,4,Cif SNP wins election
OL,6,F"By drilling in the North Sea and
OL,7,Fscrapping Ed Miliband's crazy green
OL,8,Ftaxes, our cheap power plan would
OL,9,Freduce bills by #200 for everyone."
OL,11,FResponding to the Tory leader's plans,
OL,12,FSNP candidate for Aberdeen Central
OL,13,FJack Middleton said Scotland's energy
OL,14,F"should be in Scotland's hands".
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@cO]vD@AOUvD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
