FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30515
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774828709
OL,3,CSwinney to push for powers over energy
OL,4,Cif SNP wins election
OL,6,F"The Tories, Labour and Farage all
OL,7,Ftreat Scotland's energy wealth as a
OL,8,Fcash cow with Scottish bill payers and
OL,9,FScottish workers paying the price `
OL,10,Flet's not forget it was the Tories
OL,11,Fthat inflicted Westminster's supertax
OL,12,Fon Scotland's energy that costs 1,000
OL,13,Fjobs a month in the sector," he added.
OL,15,F"They have zero credibility on this
OL,16,Fissue."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@\O]wD@AOUxD@GO]
